                     <div class="medium-10 medium-offset-1 end columns">
                         <div class="medium-12 column">
<div id="b8475267-e6f5-497c-9fdf-79e78adf83a2"><a title="TRUSTe Privacy" href="//privacy.truste.com/privacy-seal/validation?rid=ae273fd8-8196-4071-8b10-5c8750149ea8" target="_blank"><img style="border: none; display: block; margin: auto; padding-bottom: 10px;" alt="TRUSTe Privacy" src="//privacy-policy.truste.com/privacy-seal/seal?rid=ae273fd8-8196-4071-8b10-5c8750149ea8" /></a></div>
</div>
<p class="intro-head">Last Updated: June 30, 2017</p>
<p class="intro-body">Our quest to accelerate insight for security and technology practitioners requires collecting and processing an enormous amount of data. Ensuring your data is used only in a manner consistent with your expectations is a responsibility we take very seriously, and we back the privacy guidelines below with layers of security to <a href="https://www.rapid7.com/trust/index.php" target="_blank">safeguard your data</a>.</p>
                     </div>
                 </div>
